&lt;li data-start=&quot;779&quot; data-end=&quot;887&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;781&quot; data-end=&quot;887&quot;&gt;Direct and support programs, policies, and daily practices to ensure continued compliance with ISO 27001&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;888&quot; data-end=&quot;974&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;890&quot; data-end=&quot;974&quot;&gt;Maintain alignment with privacy, legal, HR, operational, and reporting obligations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;975&quot; data-end=&quot;1075&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;977&quot; data-end=&quot;1075&quot;&gt;Support governance oversight, corrective action planning, and continuous improvement initiatives&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1076&quot; data-end=&quot;1169&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1078&quot; data-end=&quot;1169&quot;&gt;Contribute to change management efforts, including integration of newly acquired entities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1171&quot; data-end=&quot;1226&quot;&gt;Manage Risk, Compliance, and Regulatory Alignment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1228&quot; data-end=&quot;1624&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1228&quot; data-end=&quot;1319&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1230&quot; data-end=&quot;1319&quot;&gt;Monitor and interpret relevant cybersecurity laws, regulations, and industry frameworks&lt;/p&gt;
