&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DevOps Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Minitab is seeking a skilled and motivated &lt;strong&gt;DevOps Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to play a key role in developing and maintaining our infrastructure and deployment pipelines. This role requires strong technical expertise, excellent problem-solving abilities, and the capacity to thrive in a fast-paced, collaborative team environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a DevOps Engineer at Minitab, you will have the opportunity to make meaningful contributions to our global technology ecosystem, supporting the tools and platforms that enable data-driven decision making for businesses worldwide. You will help shape the future of Minitab’s software delivery processes, infrastructure reliability, and overall engineering excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop &amp;amp; Maintain Infrastructure and Deployment Pipelines&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, and manage CI/CD pipelines to ensure seamless and efficient software delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automate infrastructure provisioning and configuration management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help manage and maintain development and production infrastructure, ensuring environments are stable, scalable, secure, and suitable for continuous testing and delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in an on-call rotation to address urgent infrastructure issues and support system reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Change Requests &amp;amp; Infrastructure Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage requests across systems and environments, including updates to settings, permissions, and components.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide timely support for infrastructure-related issues to minimize disruption and improve service quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain documentation and procedures for request handling and issue resolution to ensure consistency and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication &amp;amp; Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate progress and status of assigned work in accordance with team and company practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in code reviews, seeking and incorporating feedback from teammates, reviewers, and domain experts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to meet shared goals and deliverables on schedule.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Learning &amp;amp; Development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current with new technologies, trends, and best practices in the DevOps field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively explore emerging tools and methodologies to drive continuous process improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply new knowledge to enhance infrastructure performance, scalability, security, and efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Competencies (Korn Ferry Framework)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tech Savvy:&lt;/strong&gt; Anticipates and adopts emerging technologies and digital innovations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Action Oriented:&lt;/strong&gt; Tackles challenges with urgency, enthusiasm, and high energy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborates:&lt;/strong&gt; Builds strong partnerships and works effectively with others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manages Complexity:&lt;/strong&gt; Breaks down complex problems using critical thinking and structured approaches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nimble Learning:&lt;/strong&gt; Experiments, learns quickly, and uses successes and failures as growth opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communicates Effectively:&lt;/strong&gt; Adjusts communication style to meet the needs of diverse audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;About Minitab&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Minitab is a global leader in Continuous Quality Improvement (CQI) and operational excellence solutions. For more than 50 years, organisations across manufacturing, healthcare, life sciences, government, and services have relied on Minitab to improve quality, optimise processes, reduce risk, and drive sustainable performance improvement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Minitab is experiencing rapid global growth, driven by increased demand for data-driven quality improvement and significant investment in&amp;nbsp;new technologies. Through strategic acquisitions such as Simul8 (Process&amp;nbsp;Simulation),&amp;nbsp;Prolink&amp;nbsp;(Quality&amp;nbsp;Management&amp;nbsp;Systems), and&amp;nbsp;Scytec&amp;nbsp;(Manufacturing&amp;nbsp;Intelligence and SPC), Minitab is developing a comprehensive, end-to-end CQI platform that enables enterprise organisations to scale and accelerate their Quality transformations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Role Overview&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As an Enterprise Account Manager – ANZ, you will&amp;nbsp;be responsible for&amp;nbsp;developing and expanding Minitab’s strategic enterprise customer base across Australia and New Zealand. You will lead complex, consultative sales engagements focused on enterprise-wide Continuous Quality Improvement initiatives, working with senior business, operational, and technical stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This role is suited to an experienced enterprise sales professional with a strong engineering or technical background and a proven&amp;nbsp;track record&amp;nbsp;selling quality, manufacturing, or enterprise software solutions into large, complex organisations. You will position Minitab as a long-term CQI partner, helping customers drive measurable improvements in quality, efficiency, compliance, and operational performance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What You Can Expect&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;10&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Ownership of a portfolio of strategic enterprise accounts across ANZ, with opportunities to expand Minitab’s footprint across multiple business units and functions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;10&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;q

&lt;p&gt;At Minitab, our Sales team doesn&#39;t just sell software, they help the world&#39;s leading manufacturers transform the way they operate. Every conversation is an opportunity to help customers unlock hidden capacity, improve quality, reduce costs, and drive measurable business results through data-driven decision making. As a member of our Sales organization, you&#39;ll partner with innovative manufacturers to solve complex challenges using industry-leading analytics, digital simulation, and connected manufacturing solutions. You&#39;ll join a collaborative, high-performing team that values curiosity, continuous learning, and customer success while providing the support, resources, and opportunities to accelerate your own career. Trusted by more than 250,000 users across 30,000 organizations—including 90% of the Fortune 100—Minitab is a market leader with a reputation for delivering real impact. If you&#39;re motivated by building relationships, solving meaningful business challenges, and helping customers achieve measurable outcomes, you&#39;ll thrive at Minitab.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remote Eligible in the following states: PA, NC, SC, GA, FL, OH, MI, NY, NJ, CT, IL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If located in State College, PA- Hybrid work is offered&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel: 50%, including some international travel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for an experienced &lt;strong&gt;Global Account Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to lead strategic relationships with some of the world&#39;s largest enterprise organizations. This is an opportunity to own complex global accounts, influence executive stakeholders, and drive long-term growth through consultative, value-based selling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;If you&#39;re passionate about building executive relationships, navigating complex global organizations, and delivering measurable business outcomes, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;As the Global Account Manager, you will serve as the primary relationship owner for a portfolio of named global accounts, leading account strategy across regions while partnering with cross-functional teams to maximize customer value and revenue growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What You&#39;ll Bring&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of enterprise software sales experience within the information technology market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success selling enterprise solutions with average deal sizes exceeding &lt;strong&gt;$250,000&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistent track record of achieving or exceeding quota, including experience closing &lt;strong&gt;seven-figure enterprise deals&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing complex global accounts with annual revenues exceeding &lt;strong&gt;$10 billion&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Success navigating enterprise sales cycles ranging from 6–12 months.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Executive-level relationship management and consultative selling expertise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree or equivalent professional experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using CRM systems for opportunity management, forecasting, and pipeline reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong business acumen with excellent communication, negotiation, and presentation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to travel 50–70%, including international travel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sales leadership or management experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Business Intelligence, Analytics, Statistical Software, Data Science, Quality Improvement, or Operational Excellence experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity wit

