&lt;h1 data-section-id=&quot;4l9kkq&quot; data-start=&quot;236&quot; data-end=&quot;278&quot;&gt;Sales Development Representative (SDR)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;279&quot; data-end=&quot;335&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join the Team That Helps Businesses Improve Through Data&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;337&quot; data-end=&quot;601&quot;&gt;At Minitab, we help organizations around the world make smarter decisions through data analysis, process improvement, and analytics solutions. Our software empowers customers to solve problems, improve quality, and drive better business outcomes across industries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;603&quot; data-end=&quot;853&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a motivated and energetic Sales Development Representative (SDR) to join our sales organization. In this role, you’ll help generate qualified sales opportunities through strategic prospecting, collaboration, and customer engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;1wajri6&quot; data-start=&quot;855&quot; data-end=&quot;872&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;874&quot; data-end=&quot;1126&quot;&gt;As a Sales Development Representative, you’ll work closely with sales teams, marketing, sales operations, and leadership to identify target accounts, engage prospective customers, and build a strong qualified pipeline for the direct sales organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;156eans&quot; data-start=&quot;1128&quot; data-end=&quot;1155&quot;&gt;In This Role, You Will:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 data-start=&quot;1157&quot; data-end=&quot;1183&quot;&gt;Research and Prospect&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1184&quot; data-end=&quot;1766&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;152w6yo&quot; data-start=&quot;1184&quot; data-end=&quot;1283&quot;&gt;Generate qualified opportunities for the direct sales team while exceeding sourced pipeline goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;6mkat6&quot; data-start=&quot;1284&quot; data-end=&quot;1377&quot;&gt;Research contacts and accounts to identify the most relevant audience for Minitab solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;3939hs&quot; data-start=&quot;1378&quot; data-end=&quot;1451&quot;&gt;Prospect into both new accounts and selected existing customer accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;yqjg3f&quot; data-start=&quot;1452&quot; data-end=&quot;1535&quot;&gt;Utilize multiple communication channels to engage contacts within target accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;8qspm0&quot; data-start=&quot;1536&quot; data-end=&quot;1603&quot;&gt;Tailor messaging to create meaningful interactions with prospects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1s25wbg&quot; data-start=&quot;1604&quot; data-end=&quot;1682&quot;&gt;Conduct thorough discovery conversations and maintain detailed documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1psudhg&quot; data-start=&quot;1683&quot; data-end=&quot;1766&quot;&gt;Effectively manage time and productivity across various tasks and market segments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 data-start=&quot;1768&quot; data-end=&quot;1786&quot;&gt;Collaboration&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1787&quot; data-end=&quot;2193&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;8foegf&quot; data-start=&quot;1787&quot; data-end=&quot;1980&quot;&gt;Partner with sales operations, marketing, sales leadership, and direct managers to provide feedback on prospecting strategies, customer interactions, market insights, and solution positioning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1glp5my&quot; data-start=&quot;1981&quot; data-end=&quot;2080&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Partner with dedicated sales representatives to support territory growth and achieve key business and sales objectives&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1fgqsgq&quot; data-start=&quot;2081&quot; data-end=&quot;2193&quot;&gt;Collaborate with business development teammates to share b

&lt;p&gt;Minitab is one of the only software companies capable of &lt;strong&gt;standardizing data collection and analysis across global manufacturing operations&lt;/strong&gt;, from the factory floor to the quality lab and beyond. For enterprise customers, this means a single, trusted foundation for operational data—one that enables consistency, governance, and insight across plants, regions, and operating business units.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an enterprise sales professional at Minitab, you’ll engage senior quality, operations, and digital transformation leaders on initiatives that matter at the highest level: reducing enterprise-wide variation, accelerating continuous improvement, and scaling best practices globally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our portfolio supports organizations at every stage of maturity—from foundational data collection to advanced solutions like&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;statistical process control (SPC)&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;process digital twins&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;that model, predict, and optimize complex manufacturing systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;157&quot;&gt;You won’t be selling one-off software licences. You’ll be building multi-year, multi-site partnerships focused on delivering measurable operational outcomes. Minitab’s 50-year reputation in manufacturing, built through the widespread adoption of our Six Sigma and Lean Manufacturing solutions, opens doors across enterprise organisations. At the same time, our expanding platform creates meaningful opportunities to grow strategic relationships across the business over time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Minitab continues to be the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;partner of choice for manufacturers worldwide&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;because we combine deep statistical expertise with practical, scalable solutions that deliver real results at enterprise scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re an enterprise seller who thrives in complex, consultative sales cycles and wants to help global manufacturers drive standardization, governance, and operational excellence, Minitab offers the platform, brand, and runway to build something lasting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are we seeking?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are capable of owning and growing the Japanese market for Minitab&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are intellectually curious and seek to uncover your customer’s unique business problems that lead to a winning outcome for both Minitab and our customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are passionate about delivering on your goals and objectives, winning deals and have a consistent track record of 100%+ achievement on your assigned quotas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are highly skilled in value based selling of complex software solutions to enterprise accounts (1B+) over 6-9 month sales cycles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have mastered how to manage your time and effectively manage your territory while working collaboratively to resolve conflicts and ensure follow through to drive software license, maintenance and services revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;93&quot; data-end=&quot;109&quot;&gt;Why Minitab?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;349&quot; data-end=&quot;620&quot;&gt;Minitab is a 50+ year global analytics leader, trusted by thousands of enterprise customers. In this role, you’ll own and grow strategic enterprise accounts in Japan, building long-term relationships and driving impact through complex, consultative sales cycles.&lt;br&gt;At Minitab, you’ll be part of a collaborative, growth-oriented team helping global organizations make better, data-driven decisions. We value curiosity, accountability, and innovation, and empower our people to learn and make an impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&l

&lt;p&gt;Minitab is one of the only SOFTWARE COMPANIES capable of &lt;strong&gt;standardizing data collection and analysis across global manufacturing operations&lt;/strong&gt;, from the factory floor to the quality lab and beyond. For enterprise customers, this means a single, trusted foundation for operational data—one that enables consistency, governance, and insight across plants, regions, and OPERATING business units.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an enterprise sales professional at Minitab, you’ll engage senior quality, operations, and digital transformation leaders on initiatives that matter at the highest level: reducing enterprise-wide variation, accelerating continuous improvement, and scaling best practices globally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our portfolio supports organizations at every stage of maturity—from foundational data collection to advanced solutions like &lt;strong&gt;statistical process control (SPC)&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;process digital twins&lt;/strong&gt; that model, predict, and optimize complex manufacturing systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You won’t be selling one-off software licenses. You’ll be building multi-year, multi-site partnerships rooted in measurable operational outcomes. Minitab’s 50 YEAR credibility in manufacturing, through the widespread deployment of our Six Sigma &amp;amp; Lean manufacturing solutions opens doors, while our expanding platform creates meaningful expansion opportunities across the enterprise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Minitab continues to be the &lt;strong&gt;partner of choice for manufacturers worldwide&lt;/strong&gt; because we combine deep statistical expertise with practical, scalable solutions that deliver real results at enterprise scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re an enterprise seller who thrives in complex, consultative sales cycles and wants to help global manufacturers drive standardization, governance, and operational excellence, Minitab offers the platform, brand, and runway to build something lasting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are we seeking?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are intellectually curious and seek to uncover your customer’s unique business problems that lead to a winning outcome for both Minitab and our customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are passionate about delivering on your goals and objectives, winning deals and have a consistent track record of 100%+ achievement on your assigned quotas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are highly skilled in value-based selling &lt;strong&gt;of complex software solutions&lt;/strong&gt; to enterprise accounts (1B+) over 6-9 month sales cycles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have mastered how to manage your time and effectively manage your territory while working collaboratively to resolve conflicts and ensure follow through to drive software license, maintenance and services revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;50% Travel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;This position is ineligible for visa sponsorship.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;To be considered for this role, you must be legally authorized to work in the Canada and not require sponsorship for employment now or in the future.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Qualified applicants will receive consideration without regard to their race, color, religion, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, national origin, disability, or status as a protected veteran.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job application remains open until filled.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Account Executive - Small &amp;amp; Medium Business&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Today, Minitab helps organizations transform operational data into meaningful business outcomes. While we are best known for our leadership in manufacturing, quality, and process improvement, our solutions help organizations across industries collect, analyze, and act on data to improve performance and drive better decisions. From the factory floor and quality lab to enterprise operations, Minitab enables customers to build a trusted data foundation that supports continuous improvement and operational excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll be backed by a globally respected brand with more than 50 years of experience helping organizations improve quality, reduce waste, increase efficiency, and make data-driven decisions. Today, customers around the world continue to choose Minitab because we make advanced analytics practical, scalable, and relevant to solving real operational challenges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The SMB Account Executive role is built for a sales professional who wants to hunt, create opportunity, and grow a territory. You will be responsible for building pipeline, winning new logo accounts, and expanding Minitab’s footprint with existing customers. Many of our customers already know Minitab through our flagship statistical software. A major part of this role is finding the next opportunity inside those accounts by cross selling newer Minitab solutions that help customers collect data, monitor processes, improve operations, and make better decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The right person for this role is curious, gritty, organized, and comfortable creating their own momentum. You should be willing to prospect, ask strong questions, challenge assumptions, and work through the day to day realities of selling into SMB accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is for the sales professional who likes hunting for new business, opening doors, and growing accounts through smart discovery and disciplined follow up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage a healthy pipeline of new logo and expansion opportunities within an SMB territory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect into new accounts and create your own opportunities through outbound activity, research, referrals, and targeted campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify cross sell opportunities inside existing Minitab customers, especially where customers may benefit from newer acquisition products and broader Minitab solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own a small set of renewals while keeping the primary focus on new business and account expansion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run strong discovery to understand customer pain, business priorities, current processes, buying drivers, and decision criteria&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with stakeholders in quality, manufacturing, operations, engineering, continuous improvement, and analytics roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Position Minitab solutions in a practical, business focused way that connects to customer needs and measurable outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive opportunities from first conversation through close, including qualification, discovery, product alignment, pricing, negotiation, and next steps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Sales Engineering, Customer Success, Marketing, Support, and other internal teams to move opportunities forward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate pipeline, forecast, account notes, next steps, and activity in CRM tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong relationships while staying focused on revenue growth, sales execution, and territory development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Success in this role will be measured by:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;New logo revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross sell and expansion revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pipeline creation and pipeline quality

